<li class="toclevel-4 tocsection-40"><a href="#07.2F03.2F2006_D.C3.A9bats_DADVSI_:_exceptions_au_droit_d.27auteur.2C_test_en_3_.C3.A9tapes.2C_DRM.2C_licence_globale"><span class="tocnumber">1.3.2.32</span> <span class="toctext">07/03/2006 Débats DADVSI&#160;: exceptions au droit d'auteur, test en 3 étapes, DRM, licence globale</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-4 tocsection-41"><a href="#22.2F12.2F2005_D.C3.A9bats_DADVSI_:_interop.C3.A9rabilit.C3.A9.2C_licence_globale"><span class="tocnumber">1.3.2.33</span> <span class="toctext">22/12/2005 Débats DADVSI&#160;: interopérabilité, licence globale</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-4 tocsection-42"><a href="#22.2F12.2F2005_D.C3.A9bats_DADVSI_:_licence_globale.2C_webradios.2C_DRM"><span class="tocnumber">1.3.2.34</span> <span class="toctext">22/12/2005 Débats DADVSI&#160;: licence globale, webradios, DRM</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-4 tocsection-43"><a href="#21.2F12.2F2005_D.C3.A9bats_DADVSI_:_exceptions_au_droit_d.27auteur"><span class="tocnumber">1.3.2.35</span> <span class="toctext">21/12/2005 Débats DADVSI&#160;: exceptions au droit d'auteur</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-4 tocsection-44"><a href="#21.2F12.2F2005_D.C3.A9bats_DADVSI_:_discussion_g.C3.A9n.C3.A9rale"><span class="tocnumber">1.3.2.36</span> <span class="toctext">21/12/2005 Débats DADVSI&#160;: discussion générale</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</td></tr></table>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="M.C3.A9moire_politique_:_Martine_Billard.2C_d.C3.A9put.C3.A9e"><a href="/wiki/Memoire_politique" title="Memoire politique" class="mw-redirect">Mémoire politique</a>&#160;: Martine Billard, députée</span></h2>
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:MartineBillard.jpg" class="image" title="Martine Billard"><img alt="Martine Billard" src="/wiki/images/7/76/MartineBillard.jpg" width="150" height="192" /></a></div>
